DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 0;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Find all solutions of the equation \( \cos x \sin x -2 \cos x = 0. \)
$BR
The answer is \(A+B k\pi\) where \(k\) is any integer and \(0<A<\pi\),
$BR
\( A= \) \{ans_rule(15)\}, \( B= \) \{ans_rule(15)\}.
$BR
EOT

$ans1= $PI/2;
$ans2= 1;

ANS(num_cmp($ans1));
ANS(num_cmp($ans2));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
